<tr><td colspan="2" class="bline">&nbsp;</td></tr>
<tr class="syntax"><td><span class="tag">@PACKAGE_NAME@-From:</span><i>sender-address</i>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td><i>value</i></td></tr>
<tr class="syntax"><td><span class="tag">@PACKAGE_NAME@-From:</span><i>sender-domain</i>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td><i>value</i></td></tr>
<tr class="syntax"><td><span class="tag">@PACKAGE_NAME@-From:</span><i>sender@</i>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td><i>value</i></td></tr>
<tr class="syntax"><td><span class="tag">@PACKAGE_NAME@-From:</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td><i>value</i></td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="2">&nbsp;</td></tr>

<tr class="syntax"><td><span class="tag">@PACKAGE_NAME@-All:</span><i>sender-address</i></td><td><i>value</i></td></tr>
<tr class="syntax"><td><span class="tag">@PACKAGE_NAME@-All:</span><i>sender-domain</i></td><td><i>value</i></td></tr>
<tr class="syntax"><td><span class="tag">@PACKAGE_NAME@-All:</span><i>sender@</i></td><td><i>value</i></td></tr>
<tr class="syntax"><td><span class="tag">@PACKAGE_NAME@-All:</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td><i>value</i></td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="2">&nbsp;</td></tr>
<tr class="normal">
	<td colspan="2">
All mail from the <i>sender-address</i>, <i>sender-domain</i>, or that begins with <i>sender@</i> is blind-carbon-copied to the addresses
